AUDIO: 'Today, we\'re going to be talking about how you can automate any content with Poppy and N 8 N. At this point, I\'m assuming you guys are all familiar with what N 8 N is, but if you\'re not, it is a workflow automation tool that looks like this and you\'re able to build no-code AI agents and AI automations. And if you\'re not familiar with Poppy,'

[00:13] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'it is also a no-code visual builder that lets you paste in any data sources that you want and then chat with them. And when I say you can paste in anything, I really do mean anything. You can paste in Instagram Reels, TikToks, websites, articles, YouTube videos, local files'

[00:26] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'like images, PDFs, Google Sheets, Excel files, whatever you want. And then it\'s a simple as connecting a block to an AI assistant and it now has scanned the entire YouTube video, the whole transcript, the thumbnail, everything.'

