AUDIO: 'course, we can talk to these assistants through API and that\'s how we hook them into N 8 N and it gets really powerful. So, the key here is figuring out when is N 8 N actually needed. For example, something I just did is I have four of my LinkedIn posts that performed well'

[03:46] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'and I have three articles about LinkedIn best practices. And then I came in here and I pasted in my latest YouTube video, gave it to the assistant and told it to create a LinkedIn post based on my writing style and best practices. And so, I easily could have built an'

[03:58] [scene:talk]
