AUDIO: 'that\'s doing is it\'s going to really increase your context window. And as we all know, the more context, the more tokens, the more it\'s going to cost you. So, what we\'re able to do is just copy this style guide right here, which is undoubtedly less tokens than all four of'

[15:14] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'these YouTube videos. I could then just click on this T to add a text block and paste in that communication style guide. So, now rather than having all four of these YouTube videos hooked up, I could just hook up this style guide and now this'

